data.description: CHAIN OF LAKES ACCESS.  Fantastic 2 story, 3 bedroom home in fantastic location close to the water/river, shopping, restaurants & park! Open first floor layout.  Large kitchen features new stainless-steel appliances & tons of cabinet space.  Huge family room with new floors combines with dining area.  Slider leads out to unbelievably spacious deck surrounding your own pool.  Awesome for entertaining.  Spacious bedrooms. New carpet.  New laundry units.  Fenced in backyard with shed.  Oversized garage.  Golf cart friendly neighborhood.  Boat drop less than a block away!  Welcome Home!
